# =============================================================================
# Template BEZ tajni — commit-uje se u Git. Kopiraj u `.env` ili `.env.local`.
# Za Cloudflare Pages: unesi iste ključeve u Dashboard → Environment variables.
#
# --- Cloudflare Pages build (Bun / lockfile greška) ---
# Ako u logu vidiš "bun install --frozen-lockfile" i pad:
# 1) Workers & Pages → tvoj projekat → Settings → Environment variables:
#    SKIP_DEPENDENCY_INSTALL = 1
# 2) Settings → Builds:
#    Build command:  npm ci && npm run build
#    Build output:   dist
# 3) Proveri da Production branch = main. Ne koristi "Retry" na starom deployu —
#    pokreni novi deploy sa poslednjeg commita na main.
# =============================================================================

